<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-16-0847 </DOCNO><TEXT>The impacts of global technological development upon society are discussed.Special emphasis is given to high-tech research and development in Europe.The points stressed are the globalization of market strategies, the increasingcomplexity and interrelationships of problems and the need for a systematicapproach to information dissemination, characterized by an ultra-rapidfeed and feedback.</TEXT></DOC>